-- MOVES-Pimco names Joshua Anderson European Structured Product Group head
-- 
-- Tue Sep 09, 2014 11:45AM EDT
-- None



Sept 9 (Reuters) - Pacific Investment Management Co LLC (Pimco) appointed Joshua Anderson to lead its European Structured Product Group, effective Sept. 8.

Anderson will relocate to London after working in Newport Beach, California for 11 years, focusing on for Pimco's investment management. [ID:nMKWpcM0ta] He was an analyst at Merrill Lynch before joining Pimco. The firm also added five persons to its real estate team as it expands its alternatives investing platform.